{"arkId":"cl010112541","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112541","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Coffret \u00e0 d\u00e9cor de marqueterie","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Coffret \u00e0 d\u00e9cor de marqueterie"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : moyen \u00e2ge (Occident) ; \u00e9poque contemporaine (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1400 - 1500 et 1800 - 1900","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1400,"endYear":1500,"imprecision":"","text":"XVe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1800,"endYear":1900,"imprecision":"","text":"XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 5986","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"coffret","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le coffret, au couvercle en dos d\u2019\u00e2ne, est orn\u00e9 d\u2019un d\u00e9cor de marqueterie d\u2019os, de bois, d\u2019os teint et d\u2019\u00e9l\u00e9ments en corne (?) verts ; des baguettes d\u2019os, sculpt\u00e9es d\u2019un rinceau \u00e9pineux habit\u00e9 d\u2019animaux (modernes), soulignent le bord du couvercle et de la caisse. En-dessous du coffret est plac\u00e9e une marqueterie en losanges d\u2019os et de bois noirci, \u00e9voquant les \u00e9chiquiers des bo\u00eetes \u00e0 jeux. L\u2019int\u00e9rieur de la caisse est tapiss\u00e9 de soie rouge, le couvercle est peint en bleu, sem\u00e9 d\u2019\u00e9toiles d\u2019or : ce d\u00e9cor semble moderne